d264736126","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":875,"content":"找一个上升的公司很重要，可惜济南几乎不存在，所以最后等来的只有35失业","createdAt":"2023-09-03T17:39:57"},{"id":"01963de7-6b12-7382-b586-e86228e95a10","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":1398,"content":"我把老板给开了","createdAt":"2023-09-03T18:47:16"},{"id":"01963de7-6c18-713f-b9f4-be747e103995","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":875,"content":"三年了，一共涨了不到一千块钱工资，要跳槽嘛，济南怎么不跳槽不涨工资啊","createdAt":"2023-09-03T19:47:52"},{"id":"01963de7-6c63-72ab-ae3a-3bdab52095a7","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":4258,"content":"自己接单啊 ","createdAt":"2023-09-04T09:29:13"},{"id":"01963de7-6ca7-737c-993f-132d850fb32a","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":333,"content":"app开发的就业本来就早不行了吧 四五年前就没培训班开ios和安卓了","createdAt":"2023-09-04T09:34:23"},{"id":"01963de7-6b6a-7319-95b5-506ae6a7606b","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":521,"content":"地纬咋样啊？日常加班啥的 好奇.jpg","createdAt":"2023-09-04T15:35:39"},{"id":"01963de7-6cec-70e9-8a03-6f241e64b17a","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":4010,"content":"长相好的尽快找个富婆脱身","createdAt":"2023-09-04T17:02:26"},{"id":"01963de7-6b6f-7062-9e7d-b9ac9f2d3517","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":3892,"content":"分中心，我待的电力中心，挺好的，大小周，不加班","createdAt":"2023-09-04T22:39:34"},{"id":"01963de7-6d33-71b8-822c-493b253ac282","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":875,"content":"南京新政，35岁以下专科生交社保就能落户，别等了，等超过35再去新一线城市也没人要了","createdAt":"2023-09-04T22:53:15"},{"id":"01963de7-6bcd-728b-ac46-4d975d44317e","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":576,"content":"2000单/30 = 66单(天) / 3(街道) = 22单/天/街道 / 2(中午、晚上) = 11单/(1/3天)/街道，也就是说你去一个街道附近，要同时携带11单才可维持每月2000单的量","createdAt":"2023-09-05T09:09:05"},{"id":"01963de7-6a76-7392-9c70-67cb3233e8a0","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":576,"content":"济南无解，建议北上广","createdAt":"2023-09-05T09:10:02"},{"id":"01963de7-6b73-7273-841d-42653413a509","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":4165,"content":"电力的不加班？？？","createdAt":"2023-09-05T10:59:13"},{"id":"01963de7-6b77-7370-92d9-7ec8016183f2","parentId":null,"rootI